latestIgtvVideos.title: The Essence• Live with @flyingmachine_official and @ayushiamrute
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s all you need to know about The Essence, in conversation with the two emcees for the jam!

Happening on the 26th of December at Antisocial, Lower Parel.

For the love of breaking 
An initiative for the breakdancing community curated by India’s top B-boy and 3 time BC One champion, Flying Machine who aims to inspire and empower the next generation of Olympic Breakdancing hopefuls!

Featuring a series of competitions for B-boys and B-girls judged by scene legends like Wildchild , Shawn &  360 followed by an ultimate hip-hop mixer and afterparty hosted by DJ BLUnt and DJ Star on the 26th of December at the AntiSocial!
Entries now open for the B-boy, B-girl and 2-on-2 Battle categories. Enter now and stand a chance to win prizes worth up to 60k!

@antisocials @4z4di_ent @fourbyfourexp @totheculture @hiphopclothingindia @redbullindia @redbullbcone 

Tickets and Registration link below ⬇️ 

https://www.ticketfairy.com/event/the-essence-26dec2021/
